  • Class Summary

    AddItemMessage
    AddItemMessage class is the message for adding an item to the cart.
    Checkout

    ExitShopMessage class is the message for exiting the shop.
    Invoice
    Invoice class prints out the receipt with billing, shipping information, and contact information.
    Item
    Item class has the properties of items such as picture, name, price, and discounted price.
    ShoppingCart
    ShoppingCart class has a shopping cart with item and item quantity.
    ShoppingController
    ShoppingController class has the valves for actions on the Controller, Model (StoreApp) and View (ShoppingCart).
    ShoppingControllerTests
    ShoppingControllerTests class has the tests for ShoppingController, ShoppingCart, StoreApp, Invoice, Checkout, and Item.
    StoreApp
    StoreApp class has all the items and a link to shopping cart.
    Tester
    Tester class has the main function and the Blockingqueue.
